---
// src/components/Approach.astro
---

<section class="approach-section">
  <div class="approach-container">
    <div class="approach-block">
      <h2 class="approach-heading">The Reality of Enterprise AI</h2>
      <div class="approach-text">
        <p>
          Technology is rarely the bottleneck. The true point of failure lies in
          the chasm between complex stakeholder requirements, technical
          execution, and frontline human adoption.
        </p>
        <p>
          We don't install tools. We build behavioral and data workflows that
          make those tools work. Every system deployment is treated as an
          integration, trust, and measurement problem.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="divider" />

    <div class="capabilities-grid">
      <div class="capability-item">
        <h3>Complex Environments</h3>
        <p>
          Leading the architectural design and adoption of customer-facing AI
          systems within deeply fractured, legacy technical ecosystems.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="capability-item">
        <h3>Stakeholder Translation</h3>
        <p>
          Converting abstract organizational mandates and executive goals into
          concrete, repeatable user workflows that teams actually utilize.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="capability-item">
        <h3>CRM Data Optimization</h3>
        <p>
          Transforming Salesforce and deep CRM analytics into actionable
          insights that measurably drive up retention and improve real customer
          outcomes.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* --- DESIGN TOKENS (Spectrum 2 + SEO Structural Layout) --- */
  .approach-section {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 100px 24px;
    background-color: var(--spectrum-background-layer-1, #ffffff);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(var(--spectrum-gray-600-rgb, 108, 108, 108), 10%);
  }

  .approach-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 64px;
  }

  /* --- MANIFESTO BLOCK (Optimized for AEO featured snippets) --- */
  .approach-block {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .approach-heading {
    font-family: adobe-clean, sans-serif;
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: var(--spectrum-heading-color, CanvasText);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .approach-text {
    font-family: adobe-clean, sans-serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--spectrum-body-color, #4b4b4b);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .divider {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(var(--spectrum-gray-600-rgb, 108, 108, 108), 15%);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* --- CAPABILITIES GRID --- */
  .capabilities-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 40px;
  }

  .capability-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .capability-item h3 {
    font-family: adobe-clean, sans-serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--spectrum-heading-color, CanvasText);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .capability-item p {
    font-family: adobe-clean, sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--spectrum-body-color, #666666);
  }

  /* --- 📱 RESPONSIVE SINGLE-TREE MEDIA QUERIES --- */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .approach-block {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .capabilities-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 32px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .approach-section {
      padding: 64px 16px;
    }

    .approach-heading {
      font-size: 28px;
    }
  }
</style>
